# Shrinks `docker build` context. (iOS/Xcode builds normally need a macOS image;
# this file still helps if you add a macOS-based Dockerfile or shared tooling.)

.git
.github

# Xcode / Swift build outputs
**/build/
**/DerivedData/
.derivedDataIOS/
*.xcresult
*.xcresult/

# IDE & OS noise
**/.DS_Store
**/xcuserdata/
**/*.xcuserstate
.idea/

# CocoaPods — reinstall in the image with `pod install` if you add a macOS Dockerfile
Pods/

# SwiftPM caches
.swiftpm/

# Docs are not needed to compile
*.md
!README.md
